text: Once someone told me when the movie Long Kiss Goodnight came out, I had to watch every minute of it, or else I could lose the plot of it. Bot the first time, and all the other times, I never lose the plot of it, even if I would glimpse of it now and then. And it is still a great movie. First I had it on vhs, later dvd, and now soon bluray.  I just guess some people here, are they who actually need to get every minute of Long Kiss Goodnight too, or they don't get the plot of itüòÖ  This movie looks very good, something about mass control, among humans, and at top the aliens. And there is always someone who will fight against it, even if they will win or not. They believe to control humans, but at the end, you can never control the will of a man. Not just in a story, but in every possible situation. Maybe that is also a reason I love sci-fi like this. The rebels mostly show the real power among the humans, and even in a sci-fi story, most actors, usually, try to do their best performance.  So I will definitely watch this movie one day.
